OL,3,CIncome inequality in Ireland and
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland 'very similar' ` study
OL,6,FIncome inequality north and south of
OL,7,Fthe border are "very similar" but
OL,8,Fdriven by different factors, according
OL,9,Fto a study.
OL,11,FThe Economic and Social Research
OL,12,FInstitute (ESRI) published research on
OL,13,FFriday into the drivers of income
OL,14,Finequality on the island of Ireland on
OL,15,Fbehalf of the Taoiseach's shared
OL,16,Fisland unit.
