OL,3,CIncome inequality in Ireland and
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland 'very similar' ` study
OL,6,FAccording to the ESRI study, a younger
OL,7,Fand more highly educated population in
OL,8,FIreland results in lower income
OL,9,Finequality as there are relatively
OL,10,Ffewer people with no earnings.
OL,12,FBut higher and more unequal wages paid
OL,13,Fto workers in Ireland sees relatively
OL,14,Fhigher market income inequality.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
