OL,3,CIncome inequality in Ireland and
OL,4,CNorthern Ireland 'very similar' ` study
OL,6,FIn addition, although the Irish tax
OL,7,Fsystem is more progressive and reduces
OL,8,Fincome inequality more than the
OL,9,FNorthern Irish tax system, the level
OL,10,Fand coverage of means-tested benefits
OL,11,Fin Ireland is lower than in Northern
OL,12,FIreland.
OL,14,FTherefore, according to the research,
OL,15,Fthe Irish means-tested benefit system
OL,16,Freduces inequality less than Northern
OL,17,FIreland's means-tested benefit system.
