OL,6,FThe combination of these opposing
OL,7,Feffects result in similar overall
OL,8,Flevels of redistribution by the two
OL,9,Ftax-benefit systems.
OL,11,FReport co-author and associate
OL,12,Fresearch professor at the ESRI Karina
OL,13,FDoorley said: "This research sheds
OL,14,Flight on possible future developments
OL,15,Fin income inequality on the island of
OL,16,FIreland.
