OL,4,CNorthern Ireland 'very similar' ` study
OL,6,F"Current trends in population ageing
OL,7,Fand upskilling are likely to affect
OL,8,Fthe distribution of pre-tax and
OL,9,Ftransfer income in both Ireland and
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,12,F"The latter is likely to be
OL,13,Fparticularly important in Northern
OL,14,FIreland, where baseline levels of
OL,15,Feducation are lower."
